[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    176[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Suggested fix:** Adjust the estimate to "$400-800/month for a 500-bed hospital (Neptune db.r5.large primary + read replica accounts for ~70% of cost). Scale linearly with pathway query volume. Add ~$200/month per additional read replica for high-query-volume deployments."
