[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Priority resolution:** The DynamoDB scan issue (A1) is the most likely to cause production incidents at scale. The missing DLQ (A2) is the most likely to cause silent data loss. The IAM over-scoping (S1) is the most likely to be flagged in a security review. All three HIGH items are independently important and non-overlapping in their fixes.
